1 Difference between ArrayList and LinkedList?

| Feature             | ArrayList      | LinkedList           |
| ------------------- | -------------- | -------------------- |
| Storage             | Dynamic array  | Doubly-linked list   |
| Insertion at middle | Slow           | Fast                 |
| Access by index     | Very fast O(1) | Slow O(n)            |
| Memory              | Less           | More (node pointers) |

2 When to use ArrayList vs LinkedList?

  Use ArrayList when access is frequent

  Use LinkedList when insert/delete in middle is frequent


3 How ArrayList grows internally?

  Old capacity: n
  New capacity: 1.5 Ã— n

4 What is initial capacity of ArrayList?

  Default = 10
